WEBVTT

00:03:00.360 --> 00:03:02.933
from childhood my parents had told me:

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:05.454
"Do good, and cast it into the river."

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:09.022
Next, I got an opportunity
to work with children,

00:03:09.400 --> 00:03:11.639
in the hills, at The Lawrence
School in Sanaar.

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:14.971
I was the resident medical officer there.

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:17.004
I took my husband along.

00:03:17.600 --> 00:03:18.839
For the first time,

00:03:18.840 --> 00:03:21.201
I was the officer and he was the spouse!

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:24.400
(Laughter and applause)

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:30.756
I was 53 when I got my identity back.